room_title: Escape room "Quantum" by Psycho 60 Escape Rooms in Winston-Salem
room_address: 950 Graves Street, Suite H, Kernersville, NC 27284
room_description:
You and your team open your eyes and regain focus on your environment. You are in someone’s office, on your side is a person tied up to a chair with…wait, what is that? A bomb!
The timer says 59 minutes to go! You must quickly discover who you are and why you are there and more importantly, how to stop that bomb! Quick thinking and resourcefulness will get you out of this explosive situation!
